			AND(

				'Sales data'[Turkey flag] IN {"Others Budget",
					"Turkey Budget"}
			)

					"Crinoretic",
					"Diapiride",
					"DoxiProct",
					"Equazen",
					"Ferinject",
					"Ferrum",
					"Filspari/Sparsentan",

					"Fumarat",
					"Jorveza",

					"Maltofer",

		FILTER(

			),
			AND(
				AND(NOT(ISBLANK([SP_Product_Top_N_ACT])), [SP_Product_Top_N_ACT] > 1),
				[SP_Ranking_Product] < 17
			)
		)

		TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, [SP_Product_Top_N_BUD_VAR], 0, 'Product updated'[PRODUCT], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[SP_Product_Top_N_BUD_VAR] DESC, 'Product updated'[PRODUCT]
